node.text:
What is the meaning of life? Hell if we know, but here are some helpful pointers for staying #EverydayReady as you return to your everyday life this summer.
•
Brought to you in partnership with the @uscca, the Everyday Ready series focuses on tips, tricks, and advice to keep your summer adventures from making the evening news.
